Romanization

Malhaji anhado alji
Yeopeman isseodo alji
Gamjeongeun eonjena durui
Saieseo ireona juwie
Namdeuri bogien mollado
Neowa naneun da algo
Gamjeongina saenggakdo
Da gongyudoeneun pado
