Eojesbame kkumeseo nan
Neoreul bwasseo uri duriseoman
Sigan ganeun jul moreugo norassji
Cheoeum bwasseul ttaerang gata
Haeseoneun andoeneun geoseun eopsneun geoscheoreom
Machi dulman issneun geoscheoreom
Sigangwa gongganeul gongyuhada
Geu gosi cheongugin geol alge doeeosseo
Cheoleopsneun ae gatado dwae
Igeon dwae mwon an dwae geureon geon eopseodo dwae
Neon ai gatado dwae
Igeosdo jeogeosdo modeun geol hal su issge
Nae mameul matado dwae
Nae mameun oroji neomaneul wihae jonjaehae
Hal mareun marado dwae
Niga mwol wonhaneunji modu da algo issneunde

